text: They serve different foods everyday and open 24 hours. They foods are just okay.  It's located inside the casino.

Would give no stars if i could.  Came in with guest who wanted to order the toast that was seen on the billboard. Was told by Peter at the counter in an imperteous manner to order items on the piece of paper he s showing to us. If the items is unavailable,  make it known in a polite manner. Obviously, he needs training to correct his behaviour or another job if he can't be trained. We are customers, not living on his charity of attitude.
Located inside RWS casino. Great dinning area
